#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.50"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.50:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.50:0.2"
msgid "5. Rohitassavagga "
msgstr "5. With Rohitassa "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.50:0.3"
msgid "50. Upakkilesasutta "
msgstr "50. Corruptions "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.53, sc1
msgctxt "an4.50:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, candimasūriyānaṃ upakkilesā, yehi upakkilesehi upakkiliṭṭhā candimasūriyā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these four corruptions obscure the sun and moon, so they don’t shine and glow and radiate. "

msgctxt "an4.50:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.50:1.3"
msgid "Abbhā, bhikkhave, candimasūriyānaṃ upakkilesā, yena upakkilesena upakkiliṭṭhā candimasūriyā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti. "
msgstr "Clouds … "

#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.50:2.1"
msgid "Mahikā, bhikkhave, candimasūriyānaṃ upakkilesā, yena upakkilesena upakkiliṭṭhā candimasūriyā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti. "
msgstr "Fog … "

#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.50:3.1"
msgid "Dhūmo rajo, bhikkhave, candimasūriyānaṃ upakkileso, yena upakkilesena upakkiliṭṭhā candimasūriyā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti. "
msgstr "Smoke … "

#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.50:4.1"
msgid "Rāhu, bhikkhave, asurindo candimasūriyānaṃ upakkileso, yena upakkilesena upakkiliṭṭhā candimasūriyā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti. "
msgstr "An eclipse of Rāhu, lord of demons … "

msgctxt "an4.50:4.2"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro candimasūriyānaṃ upakkilesā, yehi upakkilesehi upakkiliṭṭhā candimasūriyā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti. "
msgstr "These are four corruptions that obscure the sun and moon, so they don’t shine and glow and radiate. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.50:5.1"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, cattārome samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ upakkilesā, yehi upakkilesehi upakkiliṭṭhā eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti. "
msgstr "In the same way, these four things corrupt ascetics and brahmins, so they don’t shine and glow and radiate. "

msgctxt "an4.50:5.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.50:5.3"
msgid "Santi, bhikkhave, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā suraṃ pivanti merayaṃ, surāmerayapānā appaṭiviratā. "
msgstr "There are some ascetics and brahmins who drink liquor, not avoiding drinking liquor. "

msgctxt "an4.50:5.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ upakkileso, yena upakkilesena upakkiliṭṭhā eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti. "
msgstr "This is the first thing that corrupts ascetics and brahmins … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an4.50:6.1"
msgid "Santi, bhikkhave, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā methunaṃ dhammaṃ paṭisevanti, methunasmā dhammā appaṭiviratā. "
msgstr "There are some ascetics and brahmins who have sex, not avoiding sex. "

msgctxt "an4.50:6.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ upakkileso, yena upakkilesena upakkiliṭṭhā eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti. "
msgstr "This is the second thing that corrupts ascetics and brahmins … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an4.50:7.1"
msgid "Santi, bhikkhave, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā jātarūparajataṃ sādiyanti, jātarūparajatapaṭiggahaṇā appaṭiviratā. "
msgstr "There are some ascetics and brahmins who accept gold and money, not avoiding receiving gold and money. "

msgctxt "an4.50:7.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ upakkileso, yena upakkilesena upakkiliṭṭhā eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti. "
msgstr "This is the third thing that corrupts ascetics and brahmins … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.54, sc8
msgctxt "an4.50:8.1"
msgid "Santi, bhikkhave, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā micchājīvena jīvanti, micchājīvā appaṭiviratā. "
msgstr "There are some ascetics and brahmins who make a living the wrong way, not avoiding wrong livelihood. "

msgctxt "an4.50:8.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ upakkileso, yena upakkilesena upakkiliṭṭhā eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti. "
msgstr "This is the fourth thing that corrupts ascetics and brahmins … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.50:8.3"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ upakkilesā, yehi upakkilesehi upakkiliṭṭhā eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocantīti. "
msgstr "These are four things that corrupt ascetics and brahmins, so they don’t shine and glow and radiate. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an4.50:9.1"
msgid "Rāgadosaparikkiṭṭhā, "
msgstr "Some ascetics and brahmins "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:9.2"
msgid "eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā; "
msgstr "are plagued by greed and hate; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:9.3"
msgid "Avijjānivutā posā, "
msgstr "men hindered by ignorance, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:9.4"
msgid "piyarūpābhinandino. "
msgstr "enjoying things that seem pleasant. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an4.50:10.1"
msgid "Suraṃ pivanti merayaṃ, "
msgstr "Drinking liquor, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:10.2"
msgid "paṭisevanti methunaṃ; "
msgstr "having sex, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:10.3"
msgid "Rajataṃ jātarūpañca, "
msgstr "accepting money and gold: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:10.4"
msgid "sādiyanti aviddasū; "
msgstr "they’re ignorant. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:10.5"
msgid "Micchājīvena jīvanti, "
msgstr "Some ascetics and brahmins "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:10.6"
msgid "eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā. "
msgstr "make a living the wrong way. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "an4.50:11.1"
msgid "Ete upakkilesā vuttā, "
msgstr "These corruptions were spoken of "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:11.2"
msgid "buddhenādiccabandhunā; "
msgstr "by the Buddha, Kinsman of the Sun. "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: upakkilesehi → upakkiliṭṭhā (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.50:11.3"
msgid "Yehi upakkilesehi, "
msgstr "When corrupted by these, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:11.4"
msgid "eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā; "
msgstr "some ascetics and brahmins "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:11.5"
msgid "Na tapanti na bhāsanti, "
msgstr "don’t shine or glow. "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: asuddhā sarajā magā → addhuvā sarajāpagā (bj) | asuddhā sarajā matā (s1-3) | asuddhā sarajā pabhā (pts1)
msgctxt "an4.50:11.6"
msgid "asuddhā sarajā magā. "
msgstr "Impure, dirty creatures, "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "an4.50:12.1"
msgid "Andhakārena onaddhā, "
msgstr "shrouded in darkness, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:12.2"
msgid "taṇhādāsā sanettikā; "
msgstr "bondservants of craving, full of attachments, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:12.3"
msgid "Vaḍḍhenti kaṭasiṃ ghoraṃ, "
msgstr "swell the horrors of the charnel ground, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:12.4"
msgid "ādiyanti punabbhavan”ti. "
msgstr "taking up future lives. "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.50:12.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.50:12.6"
msgid "Rohitassavaggo pañcamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc13
msgctxt "an4.50:13.1"
msgid "Samādhipañhā dve kodhā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:13.2"
msgid "Rohitassāpare duve; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:13.3"
msgid "Suvidūravisākhavipallāsā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:13.4"
msgid "Upakkilesena te dasāti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "an4.50:13.5"
msgid "Paṭhamo paṇṇāsako samatto. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
